Purpose
-------

Installation
------------

The files are configured to be installed in C:\VaultLogMonitor

If they are installed anywhere else, the .BAT & .AWK files should be 
checked for any required changes.

Configurationoptionalaction.bat
optionaltest.bat

-------------

The folowing lines will require changing in VaultLogMonitor.bat

set windowssystemfolder=C:\Windows\System32
set installfolder=C:\VaultLogMonitor
set logfolder=C:\ProgramData\Autodesk\VaultServer\FileStore
set emailserver=192.168.1.5
set emailfrom=vault@vault.com
set emailto=vaultadmin@vault.com
set emailsubject=Vault Log Monitor

Also check the following files for any changes needed

optionalaction.bat
optionaltest.bat
consolelog.awk
vlog.awk

When your files have been configured, test manually to ensure it works as required.
Finally configure a scheduled task to run VaultLogMonitor as often as is required.

